{"tid":2116070,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"中國：英國拒絕華為等同拒絕未來","createTime":"2020-07-20T02:40:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-21T08:00:36.000Z","uid":66271,"like":18,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"313a071565b7e800e6b8fad2c94c2071341cdd13","tid":2116070,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T02:40:56.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】中國駐英大使劉曉明說，英國禁止在5G網絡中使用華為的設備，等同英國拒絕未來。<br />\n<br />\n劉曉明接受英國《泰晤士報》訪問，指華為是5G的領導企業，中國是5G的領先者，但英國以莫須有的技術風險加上美國領導人的壓力，作出禁用華為設備的決定，認為英國喪失了在多個領域成為領導者的機會。<br />\n<br />\n劉曉明又表示，5G代表未來，現在英國拒絕華為就是拒絕未來。<br />\n<br />\n他指華為在英國經營多年，曾是中英互利合作典範，但突然被視為高風險供應商，形容有些人完全忘記了華為在英國作出的巨大貢獻。"},{"pid":"d273546c352b8d995eab3cd599f575dfc9fe4c6f","tid":2116070,"uid":182222,"like":16,"dislike":3,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T02:42:39.000Z","msg":"其實佢講得冇錯<br />\n拒絕華為=拒絕做軸心國=拒絕未來被美國制裁"},{"pid":"24f40f497fa5afb36ec05b20a583b4647116cf49","tid":2116070,"uid":343361,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T02:45:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"942fc77bfc6c28983ce787ea3b1863be99d91e09","tid":2116070,"uid":34755,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T02:46:50.000Z","msg":"華為唔係熱刺wo"},{"pid":"41d3c4a874d242b0243cf902b1585742bf45a692","tid":2116070,"uid":195412,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T02:46:56.000Z","msg":"佢愈講唔係會令到人愈懷疑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98324866f34f8f629a3f972e9c8b7bbfc9b09118","tid":2116070,"uid":54658,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T02:47:20.000Z","msg":"你咪理人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 成日講到自己咁重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5101606471415478c165c91e6ee82dfa993be889","tid":2116070,"uid":248786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc